16 Take three integer variables in Javascript.Assign values to first two variables. Print the Sum in the Heading tag and console window.

=>

<html>
<head>
</head>
<body>

    <H2>SUM IS </H2>
    <h2 id="id1">value</h2>
<script>

    var num1;
    num1 = 20;
    var num2;
    num2 = 35;
    var num3;
   
    num3 = num1 + num2;
    
    console.log("SUM IS "+num3);
     document.getElementById("id1").innerHTML=num3;
</script>   
</body>
</html>


